It=E2=80=99s even more bleak for SALT advocates on the Senate side, where C=
alifornia, New York, and New Jersey have no Republican representation, mean=
ing they were mostly locked out of the bill-writing process in that chamber=
 seven years ago. Moreover, the Senate Finance Committee chairman, Mike Cra=
po of Idaho, hates ( https://www.crapo.senate.gov/media/newsreleases/senate=
-republicans-slam-salt-cap-proposal?utm_campaign=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brighte=
st+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F22%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightes=
